---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { baseUrl } from '../../utils/base.ts';
---

<Layout title="Examples - UOMP" description="UOMP examples: Browser Dashboard + CLI + SDK Agent" lang="en" switchHref={`${baseUrl}example/`}>
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow"><div class="sec-num">Examples</div><span class="sec-tag">Browser + CLI + SDK</span></div>
      <h1>UOMP Examples</h1>
      <p>Three ways to experience UOMP, all backed by the same protocol and SDK.</p>

      <h2>🖥️ Browser Dashboard — Zero Install</h2>
      <p>The fastest way. Open a web page, connect your wallet, start managing.</p>
      <div class="card" style="border:2px solid #7C3AED;margin-bottom:2rem">
        <div class="card-label" style="color:#A78BFA;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">No CLI · No Server</div>
        <ul style="color:var(--mid);font-size:.85rem;list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:1rem">
          <li>✅ MetaMask / Argent X wallet auth → encryption key</li>
          <li>✅ Dropbox OAuth → encrypted storage in your account</li>
          <li>✅ Portfolio editing / CSV import</li>
          <li>✅ Agent analysis (P&L, Sharpe, Beta, MACD, RSI)</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}dashboard/`} style="display:inline-block;padding:.7rem 1.5rem;background:#7C3AED;border:1px solid #A78BFA;border-radius:6px;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Open Dashboard →</a>
      </div>

      <h2>⌨️ CLI Basics — Install & Use</h2>
      <p>Get the CLI running before building agents.</p>

      <h3>Build & Install</h3>
      <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/0xaicrypto/uomp-core
cd uomp-core
pnpm install
pnpm build
pnpm cli init</code></pre>

      <h3>Import Data</h3>
      <pre><code>pnpm cli import ./examples/stock-analyst/sample-holdings.csv \
  --tag portfolio:holdings --sensitivity high
pnpm cli import ./examples/stock-analyst/sample-risk.json --replace</code></pre>

      <h3>Start Server + Authorize</h3>
      <pre><code># Terminal 1: start Auth + Guard
pnpm --filter @uomp/server start

# Terminal 2: authorize
pnpm cli authorize ./examples/stock-analyst \
  --scope portfolio:holdings profile:risk \
  --output /tmp/uomp.env --no-server</code></pre>

      <h3>Command Reference</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Command</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli init</code></td><td>Initialize ~/.uomp</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli import &lt;file&gt; --tag &lt;tag&gt;</code></td><td>Import CSV/JSON</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli discover &lt;agent&gt;</code></td><td>View Agent manifest</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli authorize &lt;agent&gt; --output &lt;file&gt;</code></td><td>Issue Token</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli sessions -a</code></td><td>View all sessions</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli audit --limit 20</code></td><td>Audit logs</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>pnpm cli revoke &lt;session-id&gt;</code></td><td>Revoke session</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp gateway start</code></td><td>Gateway + Cloudflare Tunnel</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp gateway start --browser</code></td><td>Gateway + CORS for browsers</td></tr>
      </table>

      <h2>🤖 Build an Agent — Use the SDK</h2>
      <p>Write your own Agent with <code>@uomp/sdk</code>. Stock analyst as example.</p>

      <h3>Two lines to connect</h3>
      <pre><code>import { UompClient } from '@uomp/sdk';
const uomp = UompClient.fromEnv(); // reads UOM_TOKEN + UOMP_BASE_URL
const holdings = await uomp.memory.getByTag('portfolio:holdings');</code></pre>

      <h3>Full Agent Example</h3>
      <pre><code>import { UompClient } from '@uomp/sdk';
import { fetchQuotes } from './lib/market.js';
import { analyze } from './lib/analysis.js';

const uomp = UompClient.fromEnv();
const holdings = await uomp.memory.getByTag('portfolio:holdings');
const risk = await uomp.memory.getByTag('profile:risk');
const total = await uomp.aggregate.sum('portfolio:holdings', 'value.market_value');
const symbols = holdings.map(h => h.value.symbol);
const quotes = await fetchQuotes(symbols);
const report = analyze(holdings, risk, quotes);
await uomp.payload.upload(JSON.stringify(report));
await uomp.session.finalize();</code></pre>

      <h3>SDK Sub-client Reference</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Sub-client</th><th>Methods</th></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.memory</code></td><td><code>get</code>, <code>getByTag</code>, <code>getByKeys</code>, <code>listTags</code>, <code>set</code>, <code>delete</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.aggregate</code></td><td><code>sum</code>, <code>avg</code>, <code>count</code>, <code>min</code>, <code>max</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.payload</code></td><td><code>upload</code>, <code>download</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.session</code></td><td><code>submitDeletionProof</code>, <code>finalize</code>, <code>close</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.auth</code></td><td><code>createSession</code>, <code>grant</code>, <code>revoke</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>uomp.audit</code></td><td><code>query</code></td></tr>
      </table>
      <p>Full code: <a href="https://github.com/0xaicrypto/uomp-core/tree/main/examples/stock-analyst" target="_blank" rel="noopener">examples/stock-analyst</a></p>

      <h2>🔗 Connect to an Agent as a Client</h2>
      <p>Once the Agent is deployed, use CLI to authorize and connect.</p>

      <h3>Local Mode</h3>
      <pre><code>pnpm --filter @uomp/server start
pnpm cli authorize ./examples/stock-analyst --output /tmp/uomp.env --no-server
source /tmp/uomp.env && node ./examples/stock-analyst/index.js</code></pre>

      <h3>Remote Mode (Gateway + Cloudflare Tunnel)</h3>
      <pre><code>uomp gateway start
pnpm cli authorize ./examples/stock-analyst \
  --scope portfolio:holdings profile:risk --remote --output /tmp/uomp-remote.env
source /tmp/uomp-remote.env && node ./examples/stock-analyst/index.js</code></pre>

      <h3>Deployed Agent (Digital Ocean)</h3>
      <pre><code>curl -X POST https://uomp-stock-analyst-mvblm.ondigitalocean.app/analyze \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"holdings":[...],"risk":{...}}'</code></pre>

      <div class="hero-btns" style="margin-top:2.5rem">
        <a href={`${baseUrl}en/tutorial/`} class="btn-h1">SDK Tutorial →</a>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}en/design/`} class="btn-h1">Implementation →</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/0xaicrypto/uomp-core" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-h2">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
